		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I started out with Z80, then moved to ARM, then moved to 6502.  Knowing any assembly helps you learn another.  And knowing ARM makes 6502 easier.  Only real problem is that the carry flag is the opposite on Z80 vs 6502/ARM.

		

